metadata.name: DogeCola Ecosystem NFT #1
metadata.description: Delicious, refreshing, and transparent community that loves our DogeCola Mission! DogeCola Ecosystem is a collection of 2000 unique, randomly generated wild boars roaming on the Ethereum blockchain as ERC-721 and hosted on IPFS. We aim to build an active, supportive community for everyone here. Make sure you join our Discord.
